| BIPV glazing & power system            | $28K–48K        | $90K–150K                            | 65–68%       | —                                            |
| Aquaponics tanks & biofilters          | $22K–38K        | $70K–110K                            | 63–66%       | —                                            |
| Vertical racks & growing channels      | $12K–20K        | $40K–65K                             | 65–69%       | —                                            |
| Automation & sensor package            | $18K–32K        | $60K–95K                             | 63–66%       | —                                            |
| Airlock security module                | $8K–14K         | $25K–40K                             | 64–65%       | —                                            |
| **Total per Kit**                      | **$133K–227K**  | **$425K–680K**                       | **65–67%**   | **$29.8M–45.3M** (100 kits)                  |

**Network-wide kit sales projection** (mature, 2035–2045)  
- 1,000–5,000 kits/year → **$425M–3.4B annual revenue**  
- Gross margin: 65–67% → **$276M–2.28B profit contribution**

## Strategic One-Liner

**"One kit. One container. Infinite food from sunlight and waste — self-replicating across Earth, then the Moon and Mars."**

